{"tid":792893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打都係喺香港柯開爛屎，但一喺外國就柯靚屎","createTime":"2018-08-25T02:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T13:30:53.000Z","uid":192872,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9972cbefaf207cc5986c821e9e900c17c77aba","tid":792893,"uid":192872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:28:21.000Z","msg":"喺香港柯親屎都好撚有問題果種，長期柯親都係泥漿，碎片狀等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，色水又差。從來未試過有一條係長撚過5cm，仲要一日柯兩三次果種。<br />\n<br />\n一喺外國就柯靚屎，一條過香蕉狀完整無缺，可以隨意控制想幾時去柯，試過控到兩日唔去，就柯到一條空整25cm嘅出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，色又標準好多。<br />\n<br />\n屌，香港真係越黎越污糟，肯定有一個位出現左問題(食水？)，真係要正視，我身體已經好明顯反映左依個問題&hellip;"},{"pid":"4e0bf3c6b6a54c3ff1e9bce99ac19e8a9759f14b","tid":792893,"uid":22079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:28:56.000Z","msg":"25cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d61dbbe90c3188167b304481c6b17fcf96d5d030","tid":792893,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:33:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇圖學人開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"360c75e61a689e320c84bcf9314ce40a00d8cd82","tid":792893,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T02:35:02.000Z","msg":"講堅 痾左成個幾禮拜爛屎"},{"pid":"193b2473d0615249eebb7f4cc337193fb366e763","tid":792893,"uid":58784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T03:35:55.000Z","msg":"我都係，去旅行果陣屙親都係健康屎，一翻香港就日日肚痛肚屙，屙爛屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就算去旅行之前日日屙爛屎，一去旅行就冇事，翻到香港又嚟料。諗極都諗唔明咩原因，明明食嘢都好清淡。"},{"pid":"aa21b343d2339af8b7b8a54699f5c6ad0a8d4c90","tid":792893,"uid":192872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"193b2473d0615249eebb7f4cc337193fb366e763","tid":792893,"uid":58784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T03:35:55.000Z","msg":